4. Define the local and Global variables with the same name and print both variables and understand the scope of the variables.

def fun(a):
    print("Global Vairable inside function:",a)   
    a=3
    print("Local variable inside function:", a)   
a=5
fun(a)
print("Global Variable outside function: ",a)
